    {
      "title": "How to use this dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Correlation ID Tracing\n\nThis dashboard traces a single request through the Aspire pipeline. Enter a **correlation_id** in the variable selector above.\n\n**Data sources:** Prometheus metrics are aggregate — for per-request tracing, query the receipts and provider_calls tables via the Admin Ops API:\n- `GET /admin/ops/receipts?correlation_id={id}` — linked receipts for this request\n- `GET /admin/ops/provider-calls?correlation_id={id}` — provider calls for this request\n- `GET /admin/ops/incidents?trace_id={id}` — incidents linked to this correlation ID\n\nThe panels below show aggregate pipeline performance to help correlate timing anomalies."
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Pipeline Node Latency (all requests)",
      "description": "p50/p95 latency per pipeline node. Use this to identify which node was slow when a specific request had high latency.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "seconds",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(aspire_orchestrator_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le, node))",
          "legendFormat": "{{node}} p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(aspire_orchestrator_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le, node))",
          "legendFormat": "{{node}} p95",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
